     {q:"Why might a grid with labelled rows and columns be useful for describing a location, like on a simple map?", options:["Labelled rows and columns have no connection to finding a location","A grid provides no useful information about location","This concept has no relevance to understanding grids","It gives a clear, consistent way to describe exactly where something is placed"], answer:3}
