     {q:"Why might communities need to balance mining and forestry activities with protecting the environment?", options:["These industries can affect forests and land, so careful planning helps protect natural resources for the future","Mining and forestry never have any effect on the environment","Protecting the environment has no connection to how industries operate","This concept has no relevance to understanding Ontario’s resources"], answer:0}
