     {q:"Why might a community newspaper report on a wide variety of topics, including sports, events, and local government?", options:["Covering many topics keeps the whole community informed about the different things happening around them","A community newspaper should only ever report on one single topic","This concept has no relevance to understanding local media","Reporting on a variety of topics never actually informs a community"], answer:0}
