     {q:"Why might learning about Francophone communities help students understand Ontario’s diversity?", options:["Ontario has only ever had a single shared culture and language","This concept has no relevance to social studies learning","It shows that Ontario includes people with many different languages, cultures, and traditions","Learning about Francophone communities provides no useful understanding of Ontario"], answer:2}
