     {q:"Why might communities use warning systems, like weather alerts, before a severe storm arrives?", options:["Early warnings give people time to prepare and take safety precautions before the storm hits","This concept has no relevance to understanding severe weather safety","Weather alerts never provide any useful information to a community","Communities never need advance notice of severe weather"], answer:0}
