     {q:"Why might Ontario work to protect natural attractions, like its provincial parks, for tourism?", options:["Protecting natural attractions has no connection to supporting tourism","Well-preserved natural attractions can continue drawing visitors and supporting the tourism industry for years to come","Provincial parks never actually attract any visitors to Ontario","This concept has no relevance to understanding Ontario’s economy"], answer:1}
