     {q:"What pattern helps with multiplying single digits by 11, like 11 times 4?", options:["There is no pattern at all for multiplying by 11","The answer is always an odd number","The digit repeats twice, like 4 and 4 making 44","The digit is always cut in half"], answer:2},
     {q:"What is 12 times 8?", options:["84","108","96","88"], answer:2}
